title: Treasures of Tutankhamun, National Gallery of Art.pdf
description:
Treasures of Tutankhamun, National Gallery of Art
Metropolitan | 1976 | 0870991566 | English | 180 pages | PDF | 31.5 MB

This book is the companion catalog to the Tuankhamun exhibit that toured six american museums in the late 1970's. It is rich with stunning photographs taken from the original glass negatives of the 1922 dig and vivid color photos that are still unsurpassed by todays digital imaging. The majority of artifacts of this 70's era United States tour were, unfortunately, not included in the recent 2006 exhibit. One such object is Tut's gold funerary mask that, by modern Egyptian law, can no longer leave the country
